致上past tense就係以前發生左 依家冇發生到<br />\nPresent perfect就係以前已經發生緊 到依家都仲發生緊<br />\nPast perfect就係以前某個特定既時間到某個特定既時間發生緊 依家已經冇發生既事情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申9up"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:22:00.000Z","msg":"先謝<br />\n<br />\n有人話有指定時間就past tense 如 I went to school by foot yesterday. <br />\n<br />\n過去又冇指明時間就past perfect 如 I have fucked up Lam Cheng."},{"pid":"3eeae51018360f68e6a90cd80d5c597c05e06f57","tid":826580,"uid":4187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a5258f63935377d75ddc7a993360d1dc25288ba3","tid":826580,"uid":191738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c48ecf10a5885cb16311da7c75ee350d67c6375","tid":826580,"uid":4187,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"大致上past tense就係以前發生左 依家冇發生到<br />\nPresent perfect就係以前已經發生緊 到依家都仲發生緊<br />\nPast perfect就係以前某個特定既時間到某個特定既時間發生緊 依家已經冇發生既事情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申9up"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:22:00.000Z","msg":"先謝<br />\n<br />\n有人話有指定時間就past tense 如 I went to school by foot yesterday. <br />\n<br />\n過去又冇指明時間就past perfect 如 I have fucked up Lam Cheng."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:24:48.000Z","msg":"因為你琴日行路番學 今日冇 唔係連續性時間 所以係past tense<br />\n<br />\n至於你第二句 呢個係present perfect黎 好簡單咁講 個8婆由上任開始玩鳩我地 你覺得依家佢有冇停過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b33d30a2c9d29520e3024d02a178e004e4f1e96","tid":826580,"uid":191738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3eeae51018360f68e6a90cd80d5c597c05e06f57","tid":826580,"uid":4187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a5258f63935377d75ddc7a993360d1dc25288ba3","tid":826580,"uid":191738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c48ecf10a5885cb16311da7c75ee350d67c6375","tid":826580,"uid":4187,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"大致上past tense就係以前發生左 依家冇發生到<br />\nPresent perfect就係以前已經發生緊 到依家都仲發生緊<br />\nPast perfect就係以前某個特定既時間到某個特定既時間發生緊 依家已經冇發生既事情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申9up"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:22:00.000Z","msg":"先謝<br />\n<br />\n有人話有指定時間就past tense 如 I went to school by foot yesterday. <br />\n<br />\n過去又冇指明時間就past perfect 如 I have fucked up Lam Cheng."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:24:48.000Z","msg":"因為你琴日行路番學 今日冇 唔係連續性時間 所以係past tense<br />\n<br />\n至於你第二句 呢個係present perfect黎 好簡單咁講 個8婆由上任開始玩鳩我地 你覺得依家佢有冇停過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:29:29.000Z","msg":"咁 I had fucked up lam cheng. 就係冇確定時間既事？"},{"pid":"5e39c7e5fa0333e898a8d48d84833f7eeda39813","tid":826580,"uid":65045,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:35:01.000Z","msg":"Present perfect 你見到有present 呢個字就知同現在有關。<br />\n<br />\n雖然個動作已經發生咗，但係用present perfect係想強調action後造成現在的後果<br />\n<br />\nE.g. <br />\nI lost the key yesterday. <br />\n琴日唔見鎖匙，依家點冇人知<br />\nI have lost the key.<br />\n我而家冇鎖匙吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0892b67298543ae4cbe684242c710b202aa08491","tid":826580,"uid":65045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:44:01.000Z","msg":"至於past perfect,就同present perfect 嘅logic一樣，係想強調過去某個時間嘅狀態，而個action 係再之前發生"},{"pid":"58e3f78d8c681afa8e61836b98472e5a8a6520c2","tid":826580,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:54:54.000Z","msg":"某程度上 一切過咗去嘅事都可以用past tense <br />\nPresent perfect tense 可以用黎指一啲啱啱發生 最重要同而家有影響的事<br />\nPast prefect 指一些比過去更加遠嘅事 <br />\n<br />\n利申 唔係好準確嘅理解"},{"pid":"c7c846ba21ebcaee11477706459e3dd4522e2797","tid":826580,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58e3f78d8c681afa8e61836b98472e5a8a6520c2","tid":826580,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:54:54.000Z","msg":"某程度上 一切過咗去嘅事都可以用past tense <br />\nPresent perfect tense 可以用黎指一啲啱啱發生 最重要同而家有影響的事<br />\nPast prefect 指一些比過去更加遠嘅事 <br />\n<br />\n利申 唔係好準確嘅理解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:57:25.000Z","msg":"I ate an apple <br />\nI have eaten an apple <br />\nI had eaten an apple"},{"pid":"a4f54839c2967a632908c7eb7ad9f33d1c99795b","tid":826580,"uid":196169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:24:40.000Z","msg":"想補充一句，past perfect 有時會有同past tense 同時出現，呢個情況係用黎分邊樣野係過去既時間發生先<br />\nEg: My mum had lost her key before she backed home yesterday.<br />\n<br />\n呀媽唔見左條鎖匙係尋日發生既事 已經過去左<br />\n但點解唔係用past tense而係用past perfect 係因為呀媽係番屋企之前已經唔見左條鎖匙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df2b39da4f3250d0c4bf8699ae43c2f65376f22","tid":826580,"uid":132892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:20:33.000Z","msg":"通用黎講<br />\npresent perfect = 剛剛完成<br />\n<br />\npast perfect 其實90%時間都可以全部用simple past"},{"pid":"018a370781e64526b67e9f6dee85369f1efb85bf","tid":826580,"uid":153381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T02:21:14.000Z","msg":"個人見解<br />\n<br />\nsimple past tense 純粹表達過去嘅意思 所以凡有過去意思嘅字(yesterday, last, ago)都通常用過去式<br />\n<br />\npresent perfect tense <br />\n1. emphasize喺做<span style=\"color: red;\">左</span>未<br />\nDid you eat the apple? 你有冇食到個蘋果<br />\nHave you eaten the apple? 你食左個蘋果未<br />\n2. 剛剛已完成<br />\nI have just eaten the apple. 我剛剛食左個蘋果<br />\n3. 曾經, 從來的意思 <br />\nI have never been to Austria.<br />\n<br />\npast perfect tense<br />\nJohn had felt in love with Mary before they became friends. 表達比過去更早的事"},{"pid":"4459c0361b569d763a8044916818a552b5b24299","tid":826580,"uid":108467,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T03:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/113440_f7411de16ee6655fa82490c8e1c17c28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F113440_f7411de16ee6655fa82490c8e1c17c28.png&h=137b0ef7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/113442_fa4d69b04ff288d6750b740e43638a53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F113442_fa4d69b04ff288d6750b740e43638a53.png&h=1023ae6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/113444_f2162ec06cdc4e2bbe6a22b842a260d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F113444_f2162ec06cdc4e2bbe6a22b842a260d8.png&h=ebf38c30&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/113445_51e6823b9c2f457405b9a5dcd6f2e25d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F113445_51e6823b9c2f457405b9a5dcd6f2e25d.png&h=6b826a19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8eabfed3f18f8b2c5b6e7af05021fc5494db7de4","tid":826580,"uid":192798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T13:28:21.000Z","msg":"做過，做咗，同做咗九世"}]}